<div class='talk-article talk-article--main' id='talk' itemscope itemtype='http://schema.org/VideoObject'>
<link href='http://www.ted.com/talks/ashraf_ghani_on_rebuilding_broken_states' itemprop='url'>
<meta content='How to rebuild a broken state' itemprop='name'>
<meta content="Ashraf Ghani's passionate and powerful 10-minute talk, emphasizing the necessity of both economic investment and design ingenuity to rebuild broken states, is followed by a conversation with TED curator Chris Anderson on the future of Afghanistan." itemprop='description'>
<meta content='PT18M45S' itemprop='duration'>
<meta content='2006-10-18T00:11:00+00:00' itemprop='uploadDate'>
<link content='https://pi.tedcdn.com/r/pe.tedcdn.com/images/ted/f0244673707e0d53f813d494600e7a5bad023725_1600x1200.jpg?quality=95&amp;w=480' itemprop='thumbnailUrl'>
<span itemprop='author' itemscope itemtype='http://schema.org/Person'>
<link href='/speakers/ashraf_ghani' itemprop='url'>
<meta content='Ashraf Ghani' itemprop='name'>
<link href='http://pe.tedcdn.com/images/ted/1441_253x190.jpg' itemprop='image'>
